General Assembly Proposed Bill No. 16
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 302
Referred to Committee on APPROPRIATIONS
Introduced by:
SEN. KISSEL, 7th Dist.
AN ACT CONCERNING FUNDING FOR THE EASY BREATHING
ASTHMA PROGRAM.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General
Assembly convened:
1 That the sum of five hundred thousand dollars be appropriated to the
2 Department of Public Health, from the General Fund, for the fiscal year
3 ending June 30, 2027, for the Easy Breathing asthma program.
Statement of Purpose:
To provide funding for the Easy Breathing asthma program.
